title: No urgent relief to Wadia Group in Bank of Baroda case
description: Bombay High Court denied Wadia Group's urgent relief against Bank of Baroda, related to a corporate guarantee for Go First Airlines. Nowrosjee Wadia & Sons Ltd sought an injunction due to a financial tie-up condition.
